Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:39.50,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Final Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:39.50,Title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spring Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Arima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everybody's watching...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The people who made my life fuller.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The people who called me back to the stage...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everybody's watching...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... I can't let them down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the sound that my mother gave me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound that Watari made me notice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound that Tsubaki found for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound that was born out of my battles\Nwith Aiza and Igawa-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound that Aiza-san and I created together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound that Hiroko-san made me remember.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so scared... I can't hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just like you said. If I listen closely...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm overflowing with so many sounds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From the moment that we meet someone else,\Nnone of us can ever be alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're all connected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't leave me all alone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dummy. You have me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inside me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inside me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...You exist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way am I gonna leave you all alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reach her... Reach her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm piling on everything I have...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reach her... Reach her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reach her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reach her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reach her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reach her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just kick your illness to the curb!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then, one more time, we'll...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You and I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don't go...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pester me for canelés again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Call me to kill time again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't care if I'm just Friend A...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't go... Don't go...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don't go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don't leave me behind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goodbye...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, please take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For making Kaori's life such a full one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:01.90,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei Arima
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:04.15,Clang,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori Miyazono
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:12.33,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sumitani Junior High
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear Kousei Arima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It feels weird to be writing a letter\Nto someone who was just with me a moment ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're an awful person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Laggard, slowpoke, dummy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first time I ever saw you\Nwas when I was five...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was during the recital\Nfor the piano school I was going to back then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The boy who appeared so awkwardly\Ndrove the audience to laughter{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when he bumped his behind on the stool...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He sat before the piano that was too big for him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the moment he played that first note...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He became the object of my admiration.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing notes as colorful as a 24-color palette,\Nthe melody began to dance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was totally surprised\Nwhen the kid next to me burst out crying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet, you're going to quit playing the piano.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After influencing my life the way you did...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.83,Maihou,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Opening Soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How awful is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, welcome home, Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buy me a violin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna quit piano and play the violin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want Kousei to play the piano for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Awful! Slowpoke! Dummy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I found out that we were going\Nto the same junior high, I was elated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How could I find a way to talk to you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I'll go buy sandwiches everyday?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But in the end, all I could do was watch you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, you guys were all too tight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There was no space for me to slip into.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:55.28,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuhara University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had surgery as a child,\Nand then got treated regularly as an outpatient.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After I collapsed in seventh grade,\NI was in and out of the hospital, repeatedly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I started spending more time in than out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was hardly ever in school by then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew that I wasn't very well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One night...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I saw my mother and father\Ncrying in the hospital waiting room,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I realized that I didn't have much time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Broke into a run.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I started doing whatever I wanted,\Nso I wouldn't bring my regrets with me to heaven.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those contact lenses\Nthat scared the heck out of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eating a whole cake, which I'd never done before\Nbecause I worried about my weight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even the music scores\Nthat bossed me around so haughtily...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I played them my way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just told a single lie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaori Miyazono likes Ryota Watari...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that was the lie I told.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That lie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:15:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would bring before me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei Arima...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It brought you to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:20.62,Menacing,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From: Keiko-chan\NWhat are you doing later?\NThere's something I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please tell Watari-kun that I'm sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You two-timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell, you miserable cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal!?\NAll I did was go out with some girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should've gone with me\Nthe day before yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, but still.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess it won't take long\Nfor Watari-kun to forget all about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a friend, he's a fun guy,\Nbut I'd rather have someone more intense.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please tell Tsubaki-chan that I'm sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just someone who's passing through,\Nwho'll be gone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't want to leave an awkward mess behind,\Nso I couldn't ask Tsubaki-chan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or rather, even if I asked her straight-up,\N"Please introduce me to Arima-kun,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think Tsubaki-chan\Nwould've been okay with that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, Tsubaki-chan was so crazy about you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'd all known that for a long time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only ones who didn't know were you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and Tsubaki-chan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kashiwagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Go check on Kousei, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ask him if he's eating right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're so heartless! So callous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the heartless one. It's super-unnatural.\NDon't rely on me. Go yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Kousei... Now that Kao-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.85,0:16:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the person he was in love with is gone,\NI just know that he's feeling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't know what I should do for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a dummy, it wouldn't do any good\Nto rack the brains that you don't even have!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Muscle-for-brains!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's a little too harsh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it has to be anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right to just be yourself, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At times like these, you don't listen to your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...you listen to your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:17:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you get that perspective on romance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BL.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:03.13,Twitch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao Kashiwagi\N15 years old\NHasn't had a boyfriend yet\NBook Collection: 108
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The "you" that my underhanded lie\Nbrought to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}wasn't who I'd imagined.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were more negative and passive\Nthan I thought,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}not to mention stubborn, relentless,\Nand a camera voyeur.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your voice was lower than I thought,\Nand you were more manly than I thought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you were... just as gentle as I thought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The river was so cold and felt so good\Nwhen we jumped off Courage Bridge, wasn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The round moon peeking into the music room\Nlooked like a delicious manju bun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When we raced that train,\NI really thought that we could win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was fun singing Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star\Ntogether under the shining stars, wasn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's just something about school at night, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you think snow\Nlooks just like cherry blossom petals?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To be so consumed by everything off-stage\Nwhen I'm a musician...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that just doesn't make sense, does it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look how you've gotten more sensual.\NYou've grown up, haven't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}N-N-N-Not like I want to be able to play\Njust like Mr. Arima, all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a cliché!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't it funny how the most\Nunforgettable scenes can be so trivial?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was I able to live inside someone's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, you were.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was I able to live inside your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You barged right in without taking off your shoes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you'll remember me at least a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I ever forgot you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...you know you'd come back to haunt me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not hit "reset!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As if I ever would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it's you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will I reach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei Arima...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:23.19,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I didn't finish all the canelés.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I hit you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I was such a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry a million times over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}P.S. I'm enclosing something\Nthat I've always treasured.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you don't want it,\Nfeel free to tear it up and throw it away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Um... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go thinking you can ever be alone, Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna stay with you forever and ever,\Nlike your guardian angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get used to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Spring will be here soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Spring, the season I met you, is coming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A spring without you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is coming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:19.97,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}Your Lie in April
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:55.00,BTSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank You For Watching!
